letter ordering them to cease and desist the copyright
infringement.''
   The Washington-based committee said it has handed out 100,000 of
the cards and planned to issue another 100,000. The card is
virtually identical to the ``Get Out of Jail Free'' card included
in the popular board game but has the added note: ``Compliments of
Michael Dukakis.''
