   New York Times Co. has acquired Sailing World, a
monthly boating magazine aimed at racing and performance-oriented
sailors.
   Terms of the agreement announced Thursday were not disclosed.
   The magazine was acquired from North American Publishing Co., a
diversified publisher of trade and business journals that is based
in Philadelphia.
</TEXT>
