   The stock market rallied sharply today, inspired
by new statistics on employment that suggested a slowing of
economic growth.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials, which fell 29.34 points
on Thursday, climbed 51.32 to 2,054.23 by 2 p.m. today on Wall
